title: Intervention In-Depth - Heroin Highway
description:
Intervention In-Depth focuses on one phenomenon surrounding addiction, explores its impact through addicts, and informs about the drug/problem in question. Intervention Heroin Highway explores the heroin usage in Chicago, IL, where the highway is used to transport heroin into the city and from the city to the suburbs.
According to A&E, it's Season 10, Episode 11.
